rom, Western literary theories of influence and intertextuality.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Sep 2020) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / Asian / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUP eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000z978311070421140uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476650040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804766500423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780804766500.jpg  a978-3-11-070421-1  SUP eBook-Package Archive Pre-2000  aGBV-deGruyter-alles